original_title: อู้หูววเจ้าชายโอคหล่อสัสรัสเซียของจริงที่สุดค่ะ
overview: Prince Oak Oakleyski is the greatest movie director. He has given food to stray dogs and cats, and also organized a fundraising for homeless people in many spots of globe. The merits that he has done were thought to be abundant, as he promised to maximize the happiness around the world as much as he can. His capability is unquestionably highly majestic. His handsome ness and genetics are the characteristics of the real prince of Eurasia a.k.a. Prince Oak the real Lord Kandanai. We love the handsomest lord of Eurasia so much, and we hope that he doesn't oppress us to write journeys dedicating to him specially. Prince Oak Oakleyski once paid us for working in his constitution but he neglected our jobs. The generosity of Prince Oak Oakleyski is magnificent. It looks like he even ignores when politicians ask for election. He might not care because he's a prince. We guess so, maybe he is haughty, we may ask him someday.
tagline: Prince Oak Oakleyski เจ้าชายโอค принц оьклейский
title: อู้หูววเจ้าชายโอคหล่อสัสรัสเซียของจริงที่สุดค่ะ
